.SH NAME
get_highmem_buffer \- Allocate a buffer for highmem pages.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" get_highmem_buffer
.BI "(int safe_needed "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "safe_needed" 12
-- undescribed --
.SH "DESCRIPTION"

If there are some highmem pages in the hibernation image, we may need a
buffer to copy them and/or load their data.
